Zorian spent five days in Eldemar, though in all honesty he got everything he
 could about possible aranean sites on day three.
 The other two days were mostly so he could relax a bit and mentally prepare
 himself for what was to come.
 The idea of an impending meeting with another group of aranea left him in a
