\begin_layout Standard
It was tempting to just spend the rest of the restart goofing around with maps
 and visiting various curiosities in the capital, but he didn't.
 He had a task to do, and an invisible time limit counting in the background.
 At the end of the fifth day, he gathered up his things and set off for Korsa
 to find the aranea.

