 right after Cyoria and Eldemar.
 Even though Zorian was certain the aranea were in there somewhere, he knew it
 would take him ages to find them if he searched for them by exploring the
 local Dungeon.
 So he didn't even try.
 Instead he approached the textile manufacturer that produced spider silk
 products and flat out asked him to introduce him to the aranea.

