\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Aranean minds were still too strange for him to recognize their emotions
 easily, but he felt sure the aranea was thoroughly shocked when he spoke to
 her.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[You are Open?] the aranea asked after a few seconds.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[Yes,] Zorian confirmed.
 He decided not to mention the Cyorian aranea and his connection to them for
 now – for all he knew they might have been mortal enemies or something.
 [May I know who I am talking to?]

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
[I am Seeker of the Eight Universal Paths, of the Sword Divers Web,] the aranea
 sent.
 [You can simply call me Seeker.]

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
