 I would like to start by apologizing for the way I attracted your attention,
 but I didn't know how else to contact you.
 I hope I haven't caused too much of a stir,] Zorian said.
 [I hope we can work with each other despite this somewhat rough start.]

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
